{"tid":667529,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法改會建議擴大亂倫罪涵蓋的親屬範圍","createTime":"2018-05-16T23:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T02:34:46.000Z","uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c7b4b41c84d924ef0df73573d8baf061ae5de7","tid":667529,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:41:03.000Z","msg":"在亂倫罪方面，小組認為相關案件總涉及脅迫風險，認為應予保留，同時建議擴大亂倫罪涵蓋的親屬範圍，將叔、伯、姑、舅、姨、姪、甥等近親納入在內。同時，亂倫罪亦建議不再分性別；以陽具插入口腔、陰道及肛門等行為都受限制。至於亂倫罪是否適用於領養父母，以及其他形式性行為，小組主席鄧樂勤則指，暫未有具體意向，期望在諮詢期收集市民意見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 契爺契媽契兄妹都列入啦，屌，樣樣管"},{"pid":"381b7678f21791a584b352a2218dd207a9892170","tid":667529,"uid":134149,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:51:18.000Z","msg":"不如包埋組爸組媽"},{"pid":"c20bee9e9ebaab8a1b97473935e15c7d96a8807c","tid":667529,"uid":164799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:56:27.000Z","msg":"黃飛鴻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2b6e49adf1d402ad13d06b5777d0f97572a312","tid":667529,"uid":169662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:08:39.000Z","msg":"表呢？"},{"pid":"a1e3021444cceeb49d024c51b22f1a08e1620d11","tid":667529,"uid":39706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:09:25.000Z","msg":"咁表兄妹又亂倫?  其實無血源同過十八歲就應該唔計喇癡線."},{"pid":"2e4fc5740b8d40ba11aeb555c48dfe963ddd3db9","tid":667529,"uid":51747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3a2b6e49adf1d402ad13d06b5777d0f97572a312","tid":667529,"uid":169662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:08:39.000Z","msg":"表呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:11:57.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c862f1dfd60ba9d238aa451f4ab0243598204